  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A multi-center, prospective, observational patient registry to collect information on the
      clinical outcomes and &quot;real world&quot; use of approved and commercially available bone graft
      substitutes, autograft and allograft.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
